<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21377748">医生应该怎么回复病人「我的病能治好吗」的疑问？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="731780" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">帮一个朋友问，每次他都要和病人解释好久，不知道知乎的医生有什么好办法？</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

